===Etymology===
From {{OF.}} ''[[dete]]'' (French: ''[[dette]]''), from {{L.}} ''[[debitam]]''. A common English misspelling includes an unpronounced "b", which is an archaicism from the Latin "[[debitum]]".

===Pronunciation===
